column3: For the years ended June 30, 2024 (“fiscal 2024”), June 30, 2023 (“fiscal 2023”), and June 30, 2022 (“fiscal 2022”), Professional Employer Organization (“PEO”) revenues are net of direct pass-through costs, primarily consisting of payroll wages and payroll taxes, of $69,874.1 million, $66,731.7 million, and $62,619.2 million, respectively.
